/home/yangfp/QualifiedCProgramming/tutorial/T4-symbolic-execution.md:1:Our tool runs symbolic execution on an annotated C program. It generates separation logic assertions before and after each statement. By doing so, correctness of the program is reduced to entailments between assertions.
